            <blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">In the wake of the injury to J.K Dobbins, my understanding is the <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Ravens?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Ravens</a> currently like their depth at the running back position and the team is not expected to pursue Todd Gurley, at this time.</p>&mdash; IG: JosinaAnderson (@JosinaAnderson) <a href="https://twitter.com/JosinaAnderson/status/1432356004868599809?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">August 30, 2021</a></blockquote> <script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
